cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IT, cs.SY

The paper proposes a new paradigm for discovering sequences algorithmically using deep reinforcement learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also deals with information theory and signal processing, which makes cs.IT (Information Theory) a likely category. Finally, the paper models the sequence discovery problem as a Markov Decision Process, which makes cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible category.
